         <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
            <head>Biographical Note</head>
            <p>Italian filmmaker, 1920-1993, whose best known films include <title render="italic" linktype="simple">La Dolce Vita</title> and <title render="italic" linktype="simple">The
						Satyricon.</title> The term paparazzi comes from a character named Paparazzo
					in his film <title render="italic" linktype="simple">La Dolce Vita.</title>
            </p>
         </bioghist>
      </descgrp>
